Body: may be some connection failure error. Try test your broker connection using **MQTTLen** or **MQTTBox** with chrome extension.
Are you sure the Things Network supports MQTT over Websockets? The Doc (https://www.thethingsnetwork.org/docs/applications/mqtt/api.html) makes no mention of it. (also port 10 looks wrong)

When you load the page a call to MQTTconnect is made ( bottom of the page in code above).
